@node "Intro" "Introduction"
@next "Requirements"
@prev "Main"

     Cosmic  Battles  is  a  tactical  combat  simulator  based  on  the game
Cosmic Balance©.  In the game, you design ships and send them into combat.

     There  are  two  distinct  parts  to  the  game.   The design lab, where
you build  your  technological  wonders; and the battle zone, where you watch
those wonders burn in space.

     I  have  included  some  designs  with the game.  You can edit them, but
you can  not save them.  They are "locked" designs.  The designs are from the
six included scenarios in the game.

     As   I  mentioned  above,  there  are  six  included  scenarios  in  the
game. These  are  Escape;  Sector  12; Classic, which is the classic scenario
from Cosmic  Balance©  between  the  Enterprise and Reliant; Gamma Encounter,
which  is a  new  scenario  involving  Star  Trek®  ships; The Coal Sack; and
Escort.   If the references to Star Trek® begin to give anyone ideas of suing
me,  then  warn me first so I may strike the references from this game.  I am
not in the business of being sued.

